{"data":[{"name":"93:1","price":"朝にかけて、¹","arabic":"وَٱلضُّحَىٰ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6080,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　アーヤ*１－２における、アッラー*によるこの誓いについては、整列者章１の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-ḍuḥā ","translations":["By the morning brightness","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-ḍuḥā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1275]]}},{"name":"93:2","price":"また、静まった夜にかけて（誓う）。","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا سَجَىٰ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6081,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-al-layli idhā sajā ","translations":["And the night","when","it covers with darkness","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-al-layli","idhā","sajā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1090],[2,1090,1680],[3,1680,2545]]}},{"name":"93:3","price":"（預言者*よ、）かれ（アッラー*）は、あなたに見切りをつけられたのでもなければ、あなたをお嫌いになったわけでもない。¹","arabic":"مَا وَدَّعَكَ رَبُّكَ وَمَا قَلَىٰ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6082,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　このアーヤ*は、預言者*に対するジブリール*の訪問がしばらく途絶（とだ）えた時、シルク*の徒が「アッラー*は彼を嫌い、見切りをつけたのだ」と言ったことについて、下ったとされる（アル＝クルトゥビー２０：９２参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"mā waddaʿaka rabbuka wamā qalā ","translations":["Not","has forsaken you","your Lord","and not","He is displeased","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["mā","waddaʿaka","rabbuka","wamā","qalā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,490],[2,490,1650],[3,1650,2520],[4,2520,3050],[5,3050,3905]]}},{"name":"93:4","price":"そして来世こそは、あなたにとって最初のもの（現世）よりも善いのであり、","arabic":"وَلَلۡأٓخِرَةُ خَيۡرٞ لَّكَ مِنَ ٱلۡأُولَىٰ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6083,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"walalākhiratu khayrun laka mina al-ūlā ","translations":["And surely the Hereafter","(is) better","for you","than","the first","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["walalākhiratu","khayrun","laka","mina","al-ūlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1770],[2,1770,2550],[3,2550,3090],[4,3090,3480],[5,3480,4715]]}},{"name":"93:5","price":"あなたの主*は（来世で）、あなたに必ずや（諸々のお恵みを）お授けになり、あなたは（それに）満足するのである。","arabic":"وَلَسَوۡفَ يُعۡطِيكَ رَبُّكَ فَتَرۡضَىٰٓ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6084,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"walasawfa yuʿ'ṭīka rabbuka fatarḍā ","translations":["And soon","will give you","your Lord","then you will be satisfied","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["walasawfa","yuʿ'ṭīka","rabbuka","fatarḍā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1140],[2,1140,2270],[3,2270,3170],[4,3170,4475]]}},{"name":"93:6","price":"かれは、あなたが（以前、）孤児であるのを見出され、それで（あなたを）匿って下さったのではないか？¹","arabic":"أَلَمۡ يَجِدۡكَ يَتِيمٗا فَـَٔاوَىٰ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6085,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　預言者*ムハンマド*は誕生前、あるいは誕生後すぐに父親を亡くし、六歳の時には母親もなくした。その後は祖父の後見下に入ったが、八歳の時に彼が他界してからは、叔父アブー・ターリブが彼の面倒を見始め、預言者*としての使命を受けてからも、彼を援助し続けた（イブン・カスィール８：４２６参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alam yajid'ka yatīman faāwā ","translations":["Did not","He find you","an orphan","and give shelter","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["alam","yajid'ka","yatīman","faāwā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,640],[2,640,1480],[3,1480,3430],[4,3430,4685]]}},{"name":"93:7","price":"また、あなたが迷っているのを見出され、それで（あなたを）お導き下さったのでは？¹","arabic":"وَوَجَدَكَ ضَآلّٗا فَهَدَىٰ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6086,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　つまり、啓典も知らない状態だった（相談章５２参照）彼に、それ以前には知らなかったものを教えて下さり、最善の行為と品性へとお導きになった、ということ（アッ＝サアディー９２８頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wawajadaka ḍāllan fahadā ","translations":["And He found you","lost","so He guided","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wawajadaka","ḍāllan","fahadā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,5499],[3,5499,6614]]}},{"name":"93:8","price":"また、あなたが貧しい者であるのを見出され、（満足と忍耐*によって）豊にして下さったのでは？","arabic":"وَوَجَدَكَ عَآئِلٗا فَأَغۡنَىٰ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6087,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wawajadaka ʿāilan fa-aghnā ","translations":["And He found you","in need","so He made self-sufficient","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wawajadaka","ʿāilan","fa-aghnā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,4210],[3,4210,5435]]}},{"name":"93:9","price":"ならば、孤児については、居丈高になるのではない。","arabic":"فَأَمَّا ٱلۡيَتِيمَ فَلَا تَقۡهَرۡ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6088,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-ammā al-yatīma falā taqhar ","translations":["So as for","the orphan","then (do) not","oppress","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-ammā","al-yatīma","falā","taqhar",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1640],[2,1640,2700],[3,2700,3450],[4,3450,4835]]}},{"name":"93:10","price":"また、乞う者については、????りつけたりするのではない。","arabic":"وَأَمَّا ٱلسَّآئِلَ فَلَا تَنۡهَرۡ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6089,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ammā al-sāila falā tanhar ","translations":["And as for","one who asks","then (do) not","repel","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ammā","al-sāila","falā","tanhar",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1340],[2,1340,4270],[3,4270,4870],[4,4870,6185]]}},{"name":"93:11","price":"そして、あなたの主*の恩恵¹についてこそ、話して聞かせるのだ。","arabic":"وَأَمَّا بِنِعۡمَةِ رَبِّكَ فَحَدِّثۡ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6090,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「恩恵」のほか、「アッラー*から伝達を命じられたこと」「クルアーン*」といった解釈もある（アル＝バガウィー５：２７０参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ammā biniʿ'mati rabbika faḥaddith ","translations":["But as for","(the) Favor","(of) your Lord","narrate","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ammā","biniʿ'mati","rabbika","faḥaddith",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1760],[2,1760,2850],[3,2850,3780],[4,3780,5065]]}}],"chapter":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha","Chapter Ad-Duha","Duha","Surah Duha","Chapter Duha","Ad Duha","Surah Ad Duha","Chapter Ad Duha","Surah 93","Chapter 93","The Morning Hours","الضحى"],"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}